---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 博客
lang: zh
permalink: /zh/blog/
description: dart_node 团队的最新新闻、教程和更新。
---

<section class="blog-list">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h1>博客</h1>
      <p>dart_node 团队的最新新闻、教程和更新。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="blog-nav">
      <a href="/zh/blog/tags/" class="blog-nav-link">标签</a>
      <a href="/zh/blog/categories/" class="blog-nav-link">分类</a>
    </div>

    <div class="blog-grid">
      {% for post in collections.zhPosts %}
      <article class="blog-card">
        <div class="blog-card-content">
          <p class="blog-card-meta">
            <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | dateFormat }}</time>
            {% if post.data.author %} &middot; {{ post.data.author }}{% endif %}
            {% if post.data.category %} &middot; <a href="/zh/blog/categories/{{ post.data.category | slugify }}/">{{ post.data.category | capitalize }}</a>{% endif %}
          </p>
          <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          {% if post.data.tags %}
          <div style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">
            {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
            {% if tag != 'post' and tag != 'posts' %}
            <a href="/zh/blog/tags/{{ tag | slugify }}/" class="tag tag-secondary">{{ tag }}</a>
            {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    {% if collections.zhPosts.length == 0 %}
    <div class="text-center" style="padding: var(--space-16) 0;">
      <p>暂无博客文章，请稍后再来！</p>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
